_sText:
This map is real fun. especially if you like the original. great for pubs. everything is exactly like the original except for the crates, i rebuilt them, so the position isn't exactly right, but looks as tho its a mirror world of aim_ag_texture2.
the spawns have been switched as well. i changed the skybox and the lighting.
i can not take full credit for this map because i built nothing, i just simply moved everything around.
if you know the creator of the original please let me know his or her name so i can give proper credit.
thanks and enjoy this twist on aim_ag_texture2.
